# setup Mac DNS server(s) via terminal
networksetup -setdnsservers <networkservice> <dns1> [dns2] [...] 

Example,
networksetup -setdnsservers Ethernet 10.5.96.4 10.0.0.1

# get the DNS server information via terminal
networksetup -getdnsservers <networkservice>

Example,
networksetup -getdnsservers Ethernet

